Q3. what is numrical analysis?
A3. Numerical analysis (in the context of data) refers to analyzing numeric data â€” that means columns (features) that contain numbers like age, salary, 
marks, temperature, etc.

ğŸ¯ Goal:
To understand the behavior, distribution, trends, and relationships of numeric variables.

ğŸ’¬ In short:
